The Kick0 register allows writing to unlock the kick0 data. The written data must be 0x83e70b13 to unlock this register. It must be written before the kick1 register. Writing any other value will lock the other MMRs.

The Kick1 register allows writing to unlock the kick1 data and the kicker mechanism to write to other MMRs. The written data must be 0x95a4f1e0 to unlock this register. It must be written before the kick1 register. Writing any other value will lock the other MMRs.
